## Overview

I own these files:
- `src/shared/types.ts` — shared type definitions (ChatEvent union, TaskInfo, AgentInfo, etc.)
- `src/shared/parse.ts` — message parsing utilities (JSON.parse detection, system event classification)
- `src/server/watcher.ts` — filesystem watcher for inbox/task/config files
- `src/server/processor.ts` — event processor (broadcast detection, idle suppression, reaction correlation, dependency cascades)
